{"tid":642784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"北川景子嫁左daigo咁有銀仲要出黎撈？ 🤔","createTime":"2018-04-26T04:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T20:56:37.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0091bd2d2e88c5134937216f1de5808a03cdc0","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"好耐冇留意佢，新廣告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2110335/full/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oricon.co.jp%2Fnews%2F2110335%2Ffull%2F&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1975058a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2110335/full/</a>"},{"pid":"dfa7b99b4007e5b081668c95f6baa27292710a9e","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"唔喺屋企做少奶奶等生仔？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png&h=696d470f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceda3d97f9584500386e2a1e710bd6b3428f63a9","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"方便懶人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BYVYGyKqQWs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBYVYGyKqQWs&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7e61c6d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BYVYGyKqQWs</a>"},{"pid":"2affd86ec8db8045704e91b94d48973d81217f5c","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"15秒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OreHUfgwhCw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOreHUfgwhCw&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=45c7c70d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OreHUfgwhCw</a>"},{"pid":"14e33e106