ces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce25c22b8be80f6370c578e63caaa9364c0f4991","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/UHRh00983l8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUHRh00983l8&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=974cad9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UHRh00983l8</a><br />\n回下帶先😄</blockquote>日本仔真係可以爆籃?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿部寬或者得😁"},{"pid":"fe6bf9d25dddc683d08158a540c4e74727d69afb","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"最近<br />\n<br />\n早前曾報道，日本女星北川景子的男星老公DAIGO於4月8日40歲生日，獲日本樂隊X JAPAN靈魂人物YOSHIKI送贈名牌袋做生日禮物。原來DAIGO期後搞了個大型生日派對，邀請圈中好友大肆慶祝。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n今次是DAIGO 40年來首次搞大型生日派對，為隆重其事，DAIGO以華麗盛裝亮相，老婆北川景子亦有出席，於2013年同北川合演真人版日劇《美少女戰士》的4位女拍檔澤井美優、泉里香、安座間美憂及小松彩夏亦有到賀，眾女星同北川景子合照留念後，又大擺DAIGO的招牌手勢拍照。不少粉絲話相隔15年，5位美少女戰士依然漂亮。而DAIGO的好友、組合TRF成員DJ KOO則將照片放上網分享。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"8630dee7355b260e5e58b047b85af9a38ef339ab","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"零秒原來下年就10年<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png&h=11bd3f15&s={SIZE}\" />，真係過得好快"},{"pid":"8042a68a1775034d0ea65207cd8b234f9079873f","tid":642784,"uid":112606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8630dee7355b260e5e58b047b85af9a38ef339ab","tid":642784,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"零秒原來下年就10年<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li